{
  "stem": "25831.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "But immediately thereafter he was arrested by the Gestapo and taken to a concentration camp where he later on died.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] Everybody knew that this was staged and it was a lie.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "But it gave Hitler the opportunity to go before Congress, before the Parliament, and ask it to outlaw the Communist party in a democratic way.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And the vote was sufficiently in favor of outlawing the party.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And the Communist Party was outlawed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "It would be like here some bill being introduced to outlaw the Green Party, you know, if it had any seats already.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "And I think if they could get enough votes together to outlaw the Green Party.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "So this was a democratic process, again, in quotes.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "And Hitler said now we will hold another election to see what the Germans really want.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "And this time it was without the Communist party being on the ballot.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] It was also rumored quite a bit that the ballot would not be very secret.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "And many people were afraid to vote social democratic, which was still on the ticket, on the ballot.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "And, needless to say, the Nazi party won by a landslide.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "And then parliament was reconvened and a bill was again introduced to outlaw all parties except the Nazi parties.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "And this bill was approved by Parliament.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "And then Germany had a one-party system, the Nazis.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "And that was just a formality.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] By that time, we all began to be rather scared of what will happen next.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "But nobody really thought that anything like the Holocaust would happen.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's early.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "First year, 1933.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And in 1933 my school immediately started an anti-aircraft brigade.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I joined it.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
